	<dd><a name="comment_1240" ></a>
	<p><em><strong>dan</strong> replies:</em> Now that's a quote of the day - the Greens "over-emphasise their environmental policy"...! Never expected that one! I, to be honest, prefer them as a single issue party, which removes the quandry I have with the other parties which each have policies that I agree with and policies I don't agree with (or are just plain abhorrent). Vote green, get a bunch of die-hard environmentalists. Hardly rocket science...</p>
